d in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Tom Greatrex","Rutherglen and Hamilton West","Tom Greatrex","201638"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/63045","Department for Culture Media and Sport","false","2014-06-30","<p>The detail requested is not held centrally by this Department, nor is it collected by the Chartered Institute of Public Finance and Accountancy as part of the annual public library statistics provided by individual library authorities.</p>","Wantage","Mr Edward Vaizey","201601 ; 201602","2014-06-30T16:18:05.0690768Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/63045/answer","Biography information for Mr Edward Vaizey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/63045/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/63045/answer",,,,,"10","Culture, Media and Sport","Culture, Media and Sport","2014-06-20","Public Libraries","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport, what proportion of library users reported success in obtaining a specific book in (a) 2010-11, (b) 2011-12, (c) 2012-13 and (d) 2013-14.","false","Biography information for Helen Goodman","Bishop Auckland","Helen Goodman","201600"
